text: Yevheniy Yuriyovych Bilokin (; born 16 June 1998) is a Ukrainian football player. He plays for Metalist 1925 Kharkiv. ==Club career== He made his Ukrainian Second League debut for FC Illichivets-2 Mariupol on 24 July 2016 in a game against FC Rukh Vynnyky. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Illichivets-2 Mariupol players Category:FC Mariupol players Category:FC Metalist 1925 Kharkiv players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players
